he estate planning arena. She undoubtedly understands the intricacies and nuances of estate planning and tax law. In addition, her knowledge and experience in this area is of value to her colleagues.â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Lowrance Fisher, Estate Planning Attorney in New York, NY</strong></div>', 'Lawyer Endorsement', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-20 12:26:09', '2015-02-20 12:26:09', '', '72', 'http://lawyertestsite.com/mishiyevalaw/72-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
