n, LLP, a prominent Wall Street firm focusing on securities and estate planning.Â  Kamilla is the founding principal of Mishiyeva Law, where she specializes in finding creative solutions for clients in the areas of Estate Planning, Estate Litigation, Asset Protection, Probate, Trusts and Estate Administration, and Taxation.\r\n\r\nKamilla is licensed to practice law in all New York State Courts, and the United States District Court for the Southern District of New York.Â  She is a member of the American Bar Association and the New York Bar Association.\r\n\r\n<strong>Education</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rutgers School of Law - Camden, J.D.</li>\r\n	<li>Baruch College, B.A.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Bar Admission</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New York State</li>\r\n	<li>US District Court for the Southern District of New York</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Kamilla Mishiyeva, Esq.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-20 15:10:19', '2015-02-20 15:10:19', '', '45', 'http://lawyertestsite.com/mishiyevalaw/45-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
