 the law firm of Schonfeld &amp; Weinstein, LLP, a prominent Wall Street firm focusing on securities and estate planning.Â  Kamilla is the founding principal of Mishiyeva Law, where she specializes in finding creative solutions for clients in the areas of Estate Planning, Estate Litigation, Asset Protection, Probate, Trusts and Estate Administration, and Taxation.\r\n\r\nKamilla is licensed to practice law in all New York State Courts, and the United States District Court for the Southern District of New York.Â  She is a member of the American Bar Association and the New York Bar Association.\r\n\r\n<strong>Education</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rutgers School of Law - Camden, J.D.</li>\r\n	<li>Baruch College, B.A.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Bar Admission</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New York State</li>\r\n	<li>US District Court for the Southern District of New York</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Kamilla Mishiyeva, Esq.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '45-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-20 15:10:43', '2015-02-20 15:10:43', '', '45', 'http://lawyertestsite.com/mishiyevalaw/45-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('102', '1', '2015-02-20 15:13:50', '2015-02-20 15:13:50', '<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âTop-notch attorney. Highly respected in the legal community.â</em>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Christian Lassen, Personal Injury Lawyer in Philadelphia, PA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âKamilla is very serious and focused about the practice of Estate Planning and wealth preservation for her clients. Check her out if you need a will, advanced estate planning, or anything in between!â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Michael Palumbo, Speeding / Traffic Ticket Lawyer in NY, CT &amp; VT attorney, NY</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âI endorse this lawyer. She really knows her stuff.â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Christian Lassen, Personal Injury Lawyer in Philadelphia, PA</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âI endorse this lawyer. She really knows her stuff.â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Robert Cohen, Probate Attorney in Buena Park, CA</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âKamilla handles probate law and related areas. She is respected by colleagues and is dedicated to the field and her clients. I endorse this attorney.â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Salvatore Marino, Personal Injury Lawyer in Great Neck, NY</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\"><em>âI have known Kamilla for a number of years, and can say without a doubt, that she is a dedicated, strategic and compassionate attorney. She is an expert at taking the complex and making it simple. Her advice is always practical and on point. I am lucky to call Kamilla a colleague and a friend.â</em></div>\r\n<div clas