doubtedly understands the intricacies and nuances of estate planning and tax law. In addition, her knowledge and experience in this area is of value to her colleagues.â</em></div>\r\n<div class=\"testimonials\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>Lowrance Fisher, Estate Planning Attorney in New York, NY</strong></div>', 'Lawyer Endorsement', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-20 15:13:50', '2015-02-20 15:13:50', '', '72', 'http://lawyertestsite.com/mishiyevalaw/72-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
